info.author: Fanstatic Developers
info.description:
js.jqueryui_syronex_colorpicker
*******************************

Introduction
============

This library packages `syronex_colorpicker`_ for `fanstatic`_.

.. _`fanstatic`: http://fanstatic.org
.. _`syronex_colorpicker`: http://www.syronex.com/software/jquery-color-picker

To include the colorpicker resource, call

    js.jqueryui_syronex_colorpicker.colorpicker.need()

This requires integration between your web framework and ``fanstatic``,
and making sure that the original resources (shipped in the ``resources``
directory in ``js.jqueryui_syronex_colorpicker``) are published to some URL.

The provided colorpicker code is licenced under GPL, the integration code uses
a BSD Licence.

The provided code does not provide a version number, so we declare this as
version 1.0.0

CHANGES
*******

1.0.0 (2011-06-22)
==================

- Initial release.
